These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, april, september, march
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, milk, lemonade, hot-chocolate
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, tulip, rose, poppy
4 different pets are kept: cat, fish, frog, rabbit
1. the person drinking milk is the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person who growsrose is the person drinking mirinda##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
6. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
7. the person drinking milk is the owner of the cat##1
8. the person who growstulip is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
9. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Birthday         | february  | march  | april | september |
| Beverage           | milk | mirinda | hot-chocolate  | lemonade  |
| Flower   | poppy       | rose      | azalea | tulip      |
| Pet           | cat          | fish     | frog    | rabbit     |

