.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
City: boston, liverpool, miami, nizza
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, kiwi, orange, papaya
4 different games are played: whist, billiard, chess, mah-jongg
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, january, april, october
1. the person eating broccoli is on the far right##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the person eating orange is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing whist##1
6. the person traveling to miami is the person playing chess##1
7. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
8. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
9. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| City      | miami     | boston       | liverpool | nizza        |
| Food          | papaya     | kiwi       | orange   | broccoli   |
| Game   | chess      | billiard       | mah-jongg     | whist    |
| Birthday         | april | october | november | january |

