.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, bluemaster, ritmeester, montecristo
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, june, september, december
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, helicopter, scooter, skateboard
 1. the person drinking tea is the person driving the skateboard##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1
 4. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
10. the person drinking mirinda is the montecristo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | 7up       | tea        | mirinda        |
| Cigar           | bluemaster   | ritmeester | tiparillo   | montecristo |
| Birthday   | may     | june    | december | september        |
| Transport           | scooter         | tram  | skateboard       | helicopter         |

