.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, coffee, lemonade, mirinda
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, mauve, green, light-blue
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, dutch, thai, turkish
City: paris, berlin, prague, san-francisco
1. the thai is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
3. the person who likes blood-red is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
5. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
6. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
7. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
8. the australian is on the far right##1
9. the person traveling to prague is the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Beverage           | coffee   | soy-milk  | mirinda | lemonade |
| Color   | green | light-blue       | mauve       | blood-red     |
| Nationality   | thai       | turkish    | dutch     | australian  |
| City           | berlin     | prague | san-francisco     | paris         |

