.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, subway, tram, roller
4 different games are played: monopoly, poker, canasta, domino
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, lily, bellflower, begonia
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, biathlon, cycling, handball
1. the person playing canasta is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person driving the van##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
4. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
5. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
6. the person who's sport is handball is the person who growsbellflower##1
7. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
8. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person playing poker##1
9. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Transport           | van  | tram    | subway | roller |
| Game   | canasta      | poker    | monopoly         | domino    |
| Flower   | lily   | aconite     | bellflower          | begonia      |
| Sport         | biathlon | basketball | handball      | cycling      |

