.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-6::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, blueberry, orange, pomegranate
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, light-blue, chestnut, red
4 different games are played: snooker, poker, whist, billiard
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, soul, d&b
 1. the person eating orange is the person playing snooker##1
 2. the person eating banana is the person playing poker##1
 3. the person who likes grey is the person playing snooker##1
 4. the fan of soul is the person eating banana##1
 5. the person playing whist is the person who likes red##1
 6. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
 7. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 8. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 9. the person who likes chestnut is on the far left##1
10. the fan of disco is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | banana  | pomegranate | orange     | blueberry |
| Color           | chestnut  | red      | grey | light-blue    |
| Game   | poker | whist  | snooker    | billiard  |
| Music-Genre           | soul   | d&b       | disco       | electronic      |

