.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-7::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, pineapple, eggplant, corn
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, handball, volleyball, snowboarding
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, hedgehog, pony
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, metal, folk, house
 1. the owner of the bird is the person who's sport is handball##1
 2. the fan of house is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
 3. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 5. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 6. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 7. the owner of the bird is the fan of folk##1
 8. the person eating cherry is on the far left##1
 9. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
10. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Food    | cherry | pineapple     | eggplant    | corn |
| Sport       | ice-hockey | volleyball    | snowboarding | handball |
| Pet         | frog   | hedgehog  | pony        | bird    |
| Music-Genre   | house   | metal | punk    | folk |

