3. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
4. the person who likes red is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
6. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
7. the person who likes chestnut is the person traveling to boston##1
8. the person traveling to colone is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
9. the person traveling to rome is the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Sport      | golf      | volleyball         | ice-hockey        | biathlon      |
| Color           | chestnut | red | coral  | blood-red  |
