There 4 different types of food: lemon, mango, apple, papaya
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, mexican, nigerian, thai
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, snowmobile, tram
1. the thai is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the mexican##1
3. the person eating mango is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the nigerian##1
5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
6. the person driving the tram is the person who's birthday is in january##1
7. the person driving the snowmobile is the chinese##1
8. the person eating apple is on the far left##1
9. the person eating papaya is the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Birthday         | october | january | june | april     |
| Food   | apple   | papaya       | lemon       | mango  |
| Nationality           | thai    | mexican    | nigerian       | chinese       |
| Transport     | bus     | tram        | quad-bike   | snowmobile |

