.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, d&b, classical, trance
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, rock-climbing, traveling, video-games
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, amaryllis, sunflower, azalea
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, february, august, january
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
3. the fan of folk is on the far left##1
4. the fan of classical is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
5. the fan of trance is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
7. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the fan of trance##1
9. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |      4      |
| Music-Genre      | folk     | trance           | d&b    | classical    |
| Hobby         | traveling  | rock-climbing | drawing  | video-games |
| Flower   | sunflower     | balloon-flower     | amaryllis | azalea   |
| Birthday         | january | september     | february | august     |

