There are 4 different nationalities: indian, malaysian, french, british
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, july, january, may
 1. the person watching comedy movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the indian##1
 3. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the malaysian##1
 4. the person who likes white is the french##1
 5. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
 6. the person who likes light-blue is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 8. the french is the person who's birthday is in july##1
